These are Puzzles for 6x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-1::.
House: wooden, craftsman, victorian, gothic-revival
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, jet-ski, bike, subway
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, animation, comedy, adventure
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, balloon-flower, sunflower, poppy
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, dubstep, funk, r&b
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, bolivar, cain, vegafina
 1. the person who growspoppy is on the far right##1
 2. the victorian house is the fan of classical##1
 3. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of funk##1
 4. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 5. the gothic-revival house is the person driving the subway##1
 6. the craftsman house is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
 7. the person who growssunflower is between the fonseca-smoker and the fan of r&b##2
 8. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
 9. the fan of classical is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
10. the fonseca-smoker is between the person who growssunflower and the person driving the subway##2
11. the person driving the boat is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
12. the person who growspoppy is the person watching adventure movies##1
13. the fan of funk is between the fan of dubstep and the person watching comedy movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4      |
| House      | gothic-revival        | craftsman       | victorian  | wooden |
| Transport          | subway     | bike         | jet-ski     | boat    |
| Movie-Genre         | animation  | fantasy      | comedy   | adventure     |
| Flower           | balloon-flower | bellflower | sunflower   | poppy     |
